{"tid":2512502,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"資深傳媒人盧覓雪：「創意工業為何不是年輕人主導？怎麼會有老人家來指點江山 ？」","createTime":"2021-05-01T18:16:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T15:50:23.000Z","uid":212249,"like":89,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"807eccf77c1d45462de0103c285e6d6909de4d75","tid":2512502,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T18:16:22.000Z","msg":"資深傳媒人盧覓雪：「創意工業為何不是年輕人主導？怎麼會有老人家來指點江山 ？他們只是存在提供經驗而已。」<br />\n<br />\n日前TVB高層公開「挑機」ViuTV收視低，與ViuTV的新一代隔空對罵，成為傳媒界一時熱話。在兩大電視台大鬥法之際，網台亦逐漸加入戰場。Fortune Insight就此訪問到資深傳媒人盧覓雪，分享其對「姜濤、Mirror效應 」的看法、年輕人與年長一輩在傳媒界如何共存、廣告界如何影響傳媒生態等等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVWoSsjWaELLon4vqbywVgduFKzcgBhoCmN95V39bkWjP?filename=OVLSPGJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOVLSPGJ.jpg&h=84736884&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00cb949a6359e24d66e4f4a26bcd930ad3c563f0","tid":2512502,"uid":212249,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T18:16:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://fb.watch/5cGLMDuyye/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.watch%2F5cGLMDuyye%2F&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNo429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=857ae96a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fb.watch/5cGLMDuyye/</a>"},{"pid":"5be02775cd6922fedd7f9e430ceb95a261fbc5dc","tid":2512502,"uid":10757,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T18:17:31.000Z","msg":"Fortune Insight<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7925bf95eab363ebec0ee1851bfb95601b6908","tid":2512502,"uid":261819,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T18:22:50.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得唔使分咩老幼，分邊個主導<br />\n有料既就一齊合力搞好件事啦<br />\n後生又好，老鬼又好<br />\n大家都需要大家<br />\n<br />\n其實viutv 同cctvb 都係d 老野出錢㗎啦<br />\n但管理風格，思想唔同<br />\n出黎既效果自然唔同"},{"pid":"5ec64665b02480cfe0518b64ce3e6ce5e54c